    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted as complete. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors remain as epistemic gaps. The hemolysis threshold compliance claim is supported by simulation evidence and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification as documented in the assessment package. The assessment package is accepted for submission; the underlying model is not accepted for regulatory use pending resolution of identified gaps.",
